Here is the input.json file:{
	"data": {
		"polaris": {
			"application": {
				"name": "<APPLICATION_NAME>"
			},
			"project": {
				"name": "<PROJECT_NAME>"
			},
			"assessment": {
				"types":  ["SAST", "SCA"]

			},
			"serverUrl": "<SERVER_URL>"
		}
	}
}It is recommended that you save the JSON file at
				the root of the project directory being scanned. The JSON file can have any name as
				long as it has a .json extension.You can use different JSON files for different use cases.
